## 3. LLM KATMANI — 4 FARKLI YAPI

Sistemde **4 farklı LLM erişim yolu** var. Bu karmaşıklığın kaynağı:

### 3.1 [Phi4Provider](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/phi4_provider.py#50-639) (YOL A'da kullanılır)
**Dosya:** [openclaw_bridge/phi4_provider.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/phi4_provider.py)

| Özellik | Değer |
|---------|-------|
| **Kullanım yeri** | [OpenClawRuntime](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/runtime.py#83-573) → CLI interaktif komutlar |
| **Bağlantı** | [aiohttp](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py#272-363) ile doğrudan HTTP POST |
| **Varsayılan** | Gemini API (`generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai`) |
| **Fallback** | Ollama (`localhost:11434`) |
| **Retry** | `retry_count=5`, basit döngü ile tekrar deneme |
| **Tool calling** | Native (API'den `tool_calls`) + Prompt-based fallback (JSON parse) |
| **Context yönetimi** | Yok — runtime'daki [_trim_conversation_if_needed()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/runtime.py#408-446) yapıyor |

**Mantık:** Provider listesi oluşturur (primary + ollama), sırayla dener. Provider config'ten `temperature`, `max_tokens`, `timeout` alınır.

### 3.2 [OpenRouterClient](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py#66-512) (YOL B'de kullanılır)
**Dosya:** [router/openrouter_client.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py)

| Özellik | Değer |
|---------|-------|
| **Kullanım yeri** | [RedClawPentest](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/pentest.py#45-977) → Otonom pentest pipeline |
| **Dual-Brain** | Brain (`gpt-oss-120B:free`) + Hands (`qwen3-coder:free`) |
| **Bağlantı** | [aiohttp](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py#272-363) ile OpenRouter API'ye POST |
| **API Key** | `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` env → `~/.redclaw/api_key.txt` |
| **LLMClient** | **OPSIYONEL** — pentest.py `llm_client=None` ile oluşturur! |
| **Retry** | `retry_count=5` sayılır ama **LLMClient yoksa retry mekanizması çalışmaz** |

**Dual-Brain Sistemi:**
- `BRAIN = ModelProfile("Brain", "openai/gpt-oss-120B:free", temp=0.3, max_tokens=16384)`
- `HANDS = ModelProfile("Hands", "qwen/qwen3-coder:free", temp=0.1, max_tokens=16384)`
- [call_brain()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py#376-408) → Stratejik planlama, analiz
- [call_hands()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py#404-454) → Kod üretimi, exploit yazımı
- [dual_brain()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py#461-484) → Brain planlar → Hands kodlar → Brain review eder

