| **Message fix** | [fix_message_list()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/llm_client.py#124-193) — orphan tool_calls, duplicate mesajlar temizlenir |
| **Backend** | `litellm` kütüphanesi |

> **KRİTİK:** [LLMClient](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/llm_client.py#359-832) oluşturulup [cli/app.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/cli/app.py)'ye geçirilir ama **NE pentest.py NE DE runtime.py bunu kullanır!**

