## 6. AGENT FRAMEWORK

### 6.1 BaseAgent ([agents/base_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/base_agent.py))

**ReAct döngüsü:**
```
OBSERVE → THINK → ACT → EVALUATE → (tekrar veya COMPLETE)
```

- Abstract sınıf, `ABC` ile yazılmış
- 4 abstract metod: [observe()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/phase_agents.py#103-105), [think()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/base_agent.py#164-168), [act()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/base_agent.py#169-173), [evaluate()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/phase_agents.py#159-169)
- `_max_iterations = 30`
- [_should_complete()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/base_agent.py#186-188) → Decision'da "COMPLETE" varsa dur
- [_is_phase_complete()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/base_agent.py#189-191) → Evaluation'da "PHASE_COMPLETE" varsa dur

