### 6.3 TeamLead ([agents/team_lead.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/team_lead.py))

| Özellik | Detay |
|---------|-------|
| **İşlev** | Task decomposition → teammate spawning → monitoring → synthesis |
| **Bağımlılıklar** | [OpenRouterClient](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/openrouter_client.py#66-512), [ModelAlloyRouter](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/router/model_alloy.py#260-374), [MemAgent](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/memory/memagent.py#31-352), [Mailbox](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/mailbox.py#27-191), [SharedTaskList](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/shared_task_list.py#30-235), [LockManager](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/agents/lock_manager.py#18-142) |
| **Kullanım** | **Hiçbir yerde çağrılmıyor!** Ne CLI ne pentest pipeline TeamLead kullanıyor. |

**TeamLead akışı (teorik):**
```
1. orchestrate(user_request)
2. decompose_task() → Brain LLM ile task'ı alt görevlere böl
3. spawn_teammate() → Her alt görev için worker coroutine oluştur
4. monitor_progress() → Mailbox'tan mesajları oku, takılmış worker'ları tespit et
5. synthesize_results() → Brain ile tüm sonuçları birleştir
6. cleanup() → Worker'ları temizle
```

