## 7. GÜVENLİK KATMANI

### 7.1 GuardianRails ([core/guardian.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/core/guardian.py))

| Özellik | Detay |
|---------|-------|
| **Blocklist** | `rm -rf`, `mkfs`, [dd](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/memory/memory_rag.py#42-45), [shutdown](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/runtime.py#542-549), `reboot`, `iptables -F`, [format](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/openclaw/.swiftformat) |
| **Suspicious patterns** | Regex: `chmod -R 777 /`, `curl|bash`, `wget -O - | sh` |
| **Scope kontrolü** | IP/CIDR tabanlı — hedef scope dışındaysa BLOCKED |
| **Rate limiting** | Dakikada max 100 komut |
| **Risk classification** | SAFE → LOW → MEDIUM → HIGH → CRITICAL → BLOCKED |
| **Audit logging** | Her komut kaydedilir (timestamp, risk, allowed/denied) |
| **Approval callback** | HIGH risk komutlarda callback fonksiyonu çağrılabilir |

**Entegrasyon:** Sadece [ToolBridge](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/openclaw_bridge/tool_bridge.py#43-221) kullanır. [pentest.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/run_pentest.py) **GuardianRails'i bypass eder.**

