## 8. RAPORLAMA KATMANI

### 8.1 CausalChainReport ([reporting/causal_chain.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/reporting/causal_chain.py))

**Format:** WHY → WHAT → HOW → PROOF → FIX

Her finding için:
- **WHY:** Root cause analysis
- **WHAT:** CVE, CVSS, Service, Impact
- **HOW:** Step-by-step exploitation path
- **PROOF:** Command çıktısı, screenshot, log
- **FIX:** Remediation önerisi

**Çıktı:** Text + JSON, `~/.redclaw/engagements/<target>/reports/` klasörüne yazılır.

### 8.2 Report Generator ([reporting/generator.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/reporting/generator.py))

