## 9. ZERO-DAY HUNTER ([zeroday_hunter.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/src/redclaw/zeroday_hunter.py))

| Özellik | Detay |
|---------|-------|
| **LLM kullanır mı?** | **HAYIR — tamamen Python stdlib** |
| **Bağımlılık** | `socket`, `http.client`, `struct` — harici kütüphane yok |
| **Protokoller** | FTP, HTTP, MySQL, SSH, VNC, Telnet |

**Her protokol için yapılanlar:**

| Protokol | Testler |
|----------|---------|
| **FTP** | Backdoor tespiti (vsFTPd 2.3.4 trigger), oversized USER/PASS, directory traversal, anonymous login, SITE EXEC injection |
| **HTTP** | Path traversal (`../../etc/passwd`), host header injection, oversized headers, verb tampering (TRACE, OPTIONS, PROPFIND), HTTP/0.9 downgrade, cache poisoning |
| **MySQL** | Auth bypass payloads, oversized username, version extraction, COM_PING/COM_QUERY |
| **SSH** | Banner grabbing, oversized ID string, uzun key exchange, NULL cipher teklifi |
| **VNC** | Auth bypass (SecurityType=1), oversized shared flag, invalid protocol version |
| **Telnet** | Login fuzzing, command injection payloads, oversized input |

**Çıktı:** `anomalies` listesi → [pentest.py](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/Desktop/SparkStack%20Systsems/Red%20Shadow%20Documents/red_shadow_v2.0/Red-Shadow/run_pentest.py)'ye `Dict` olarak döner.

